PoweredActivity
The PoweredActivity class represents an activity that uses a specific piece of equipment, such as biking with a bike or running on a treadmill.
TransportMode
The TransportMode enumeration lists the standard ways a person can move during an activity in this program.
ValidEquipment
The ValidEquipment class represents a piece of equipment that can be used in an activity, such as a bike, treadmill, or soccer ball.
